---
const APP_URL = "https://app.nidero.se";
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="sv" data-theme="light">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<title>Nidero — Ordning på familjens ekonomi</title>
<meta name="description" content="Ett lugnt system för familjens ekonomi. Löner, lån, sparande och balansräkning — på ett ställe, för båda i hushållet."/>
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg"/>
<meta property="og:title" content="Nidero — Ordning på familjens ekonomi"/>
<meta property="og:description" content="Nidero samlar budget, sparande, lån och tillgångar på ett ställe. Byggt för svenska familjer."/>
<meta property="og:image" content="/screenshot-desktop2.png"/>
<meta property="og:type" content="website"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
/* ── TOKENS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
:root {
  --font-ui:      'Geist', ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif;
  --font-display: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
  --font-mono:    'Geist Mono', ui-monospace, 'SF Mono', monospace;
  --space-1:4px;--space-2:8px;--space-3:12px;--space-4:16px;
  --space-5:20px;--space-6:24px;--space-8:32px;--space-10:40px;
  --space-12:48px;--space-16:64px;--space-20:80px;--space-24:96px;
  --radius-xs:4px;--radius-sm:6px;--radius-md:10px;
  --radius-lg:14px;--radius-xl:20px;--radius-2xl:28px;--radius-pill:999px;
  --text-xs:11px;--text-sm:13px;--text-base:15px;--text-md:17px;
  --text-lg:20px;--text-xl:24px;--text-2xl:30px;--text-3xl:38px;
  --text-4xl:52px;
  --brand-500: oklch(0.58 0.13 252);
  --brand-600: oklch(0.50 0.13 252);
  --brand-700: oklch(0.42 0.12 252);
  --accent-500: oklch(0.68 0.11 55);
  --accent-600: oklch(0.60 0.12 55);
  --success: oklch(0.62 0.12 155);
  --warning: oklch(0.72 0.13 75);
  --danger:  oklch(0.60 0.18 22);
  --member-1: oklch(0.62 0.14 252);
  --member-2: oklch(0.62 0.14 28);
  --member-4: oklch(0.72 0.13 75);
  --chart-income:  oklch(0.65 0.12 155);
  --chart-expense: oklch(0.62 0.16 22);
  --chart-saving:  oklch(0.62 0.13 252);
  --ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.22,0.61,0.36,1);
  --dur-fast: 120ms;--dur-base: 200ms;
}
:root {
  --bg-canvas:    oklch(0.985 0.003 90);
  --bg-page:      oklch(0.978 0.005 80);
  --bg-surface:   oklch(1 0 0);
  --bg-surface-2: oklch(0.97 0.005 90);
  --bg-input:     oklch(0.98 0.004 90);
  --bg-hover:     oklch(0.95 0.005 90);
  --bg-ink:       oklch(0.20 0.012 250);
  --bg-band:      oklch(0.95 0.012 80);
  --fg-primary:   oklch(0.20 0.012 250);
  --fg-secondary: oklch(0.40 0.010 250);
  --fg-tertiary:  oklch(0.55 0.008 250);
  --fg-muted:     oklch(0.68 0.008 250);
  --fg-on-ink:    oklch(0.96 0.005 250);
  --border:        oklch(0.90 0.006 250);
  --border-strong: oklch(0.78 0.008 250);
  --border-subtle: oklch(0.94 0.005 250);
  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(20,30,50,0.04);
  --shadow-md: 0 4px 14px rgba(20,30,50,0.06);
  --shadow-lg: 0 18px 48px rgba(20,30,50,0.10);
  --shadow-xl: 0 32px 80px rgba(20,30,50,0.14);
  --logo-accent: oklch(0.60 0.13 55);
  color-scheme: light;
}
/* ── BASE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:1.55;color:var(--fg-primary);background:var(--bg-page);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;font-feature-settings:"ss01","cv11";font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{margin:0;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.015em}
p{margin:0}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
img,svg{display:block;max-width:100%}
.num{font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;font-feature-settings:"tnum"}
.mono{font-family:var(--font-mono)}
.serif{font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:400}
.muted{color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
/* ── LAYOUT ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.wrap{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 var(--space-8)}
.wrap-narrow{max-width:920px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 var(--space-8)}
.section{padding:var(--space-24) 0}
.section-tight{padding:var(--space-16) 0}
.section-header{margin-bottom:var(--space-12);max-width:720px}
.section-eyebrow{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary);margin-bottom:var(--space-4);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;white-space:nowrap}
.section-eyebrow::before{content:"";width:22px;height:1px;background:var(--border-strong)}
.section-title{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-4xl);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.02em;font-weight:400;color:var(--fg-primary)}
.section-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--brand-500)}
.section-lead{margin-top:var(--space-5);color:var(--fg-secondary);font-size:var(--text-md);max-width:60ch;line-height:1.55}
/* ── TOPBAR ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.topbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:color-mix(in oklch,var(--bg-page) 82%,transparent);backdrop-filter:saturate(140%) blur(14px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:saturate(140%) blur(14px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
.topbar-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:var(--space-4) var(--space-8);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:var(--space-6)}
/* ── Logo pill-badge · Gradient·brand variant (§5c) ───────────── */
.brand-pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:6px 14px 6px 9px;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#5C7AE0 0%,#3D5BC7 55%,#2A3F9E 100%);border-radius:var(--radius-pill);color:#fff;text-decoration:none;box-shadow:0 6px 16px color-mix(in oklch,#3D5BC7 30%,transparent);flex-shrink:0}
.brand-pill-text{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:21px;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.015em}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-2)}
.nav-links a{font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--fg-secondary);padding:8px 14px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);white-space:nowrap;transition:color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),background var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out)}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--fg-primary);background:var(--bg-hover)}
.nav-actions{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-3)}
.theme-toggle{width:36px;height:36px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-pill);color:var(--fg-secondary);cursor:pointer;transition:color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),background var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out)}
/* ── BUTTONS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;height:44px;padding:0 20px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);font:inherit;font-size:var(--text-sm);font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid transparent;white-space:nowrap;transition:background var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out)}
.btn-primary{background:var(--bg-ink);color:var(--fg-on-ink)}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--brand-600)}
.btn-secondary{background:transparent;color:var(--fg-primary);border-color:var(--border-strong)}
.btn-secondary:hover{background:var(--bg-hover);border-color:var(--fg-primary)}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.btn-ghost:hover{color:var(--fg-primary);background:var(--bg-hover)}
.btn-sm{height:36px;padding:0 14px;font-size:var(--text-sm)}
.btn-lg{height:52px;padding:0 26px;font-size:var(--text-md)}
.arrow{width:14px;height:14px}
.sr-only{position:absolute;width:1px;height:1px;padding:0;margin:-1px;overflow:hidden;clip:rect(0,0,0,0);border:0}
/* ── HERO FORM ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero-form{margin-top:var(--space-8);display:flex;gap:8px;max-width:480px;background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-pill);padding:6px 6px 6px 18px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm);transition:border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),box-shadow var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out)}
.hero-form:focus-within{border-color:var(--brand-500);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px color-mix(in oklch,var(--brand-500) 18%,transparent)}
.hero-form input{flex:1;min-width:0;background:transparent;border:0;outline:0;font:inherit;font-size:var(--text-md);color:var(--fg-primary);padding:0}
.hero-form input::placeholder{color:var(--fg-muted)}
.hero-form button{flex-shrink:0;height:44px}
.hero-form-note{margin-top:var(--space-3);font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--fg-muted)}
.hero-form.success{border-color:var(--success);background:color-mix(in oklch,var(--success) 6%,var(--bg-surface))}
/* ── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero{padding:var(--space-20) 0 var(--space-12);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero::before{content:"";position:absolute;inset:-20% -10% auto auto;width:720px;height:720px;background:radial-gradient(closest-side,color-mix(in oklch,var(--accent-500) 28%,transparent) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;z-index:0;filter:blur(20px)}
.hero-grid{position:relative;z-index:1;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space-12);align-items:center}
@media(min-width:980px){.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1.05fr 1fr;gap:var(--space-16)}}
.hero-eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:6px 14px 6px 6px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-pill);background:var(--bg-surface);font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--fg-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--space-6)}
.hero-eyebrow .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--success);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px color-mix(in oklch,var(--success) 18%,transparent)}
.hero-eyebrow strong{color:var(--fg-primary);font-weight:500}
.hero h1{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(48px,8vw,84px);line-height:0.96;letter-spacing:-0.025em;font-weight:400;color:var(--fg-primary)}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--brand-500)}
.hero-lead{margin-top:var(--space-6);font-size:var(--text-lg);color:var(--fg-secondary);line-height:1.5;max-width:48ch}
.hero-cta{margin-top:var(--space-8);display:flex;gap:var(--space-3);flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-meta{margin-top:var(--space-10);display:flex;gap:var(--space-8);flex-wrap:wrap;border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);padding-top:var(--space-6)}
.hero-meta-item .label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.10em;color:var(--fg-muted)}
.hero-meta-item .value{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:28px;margin-top:2px;color:var(--fg-primary)}
/* ── HERO VISUAL ────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero-visual{position:relative;perspective:1800px;isolation:isolate}
.hero-card{background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl);overflow:hidden;transform:rotate(-1.2deg)}
.hero-card-2{position:absolute;right:-20px;bottom:-30px;width:62%;background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);padding:16px 18px;transform:rotate(2deg);z-index:2}
.hero-card-3{position:absolute;left:-28px;top:18%;width:50%;background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md);padding:14px 16px;transform:rotate(-3deg);z-index:1}
/* ── MOCK PRIMITIVES ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.mock{background:var(--bg-canvas);color:var(--fg-primary);font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:12px;line-height:1.4}
.mock-chrome{height:32px;background:var(--bg-surface-2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 12px;gap:8px}
.mock-dots{display:flex;gap:6px}
.mock-dot{width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--border-strong)}
.mock-dot.r{background:#ed6a5e}.mock-dot.y{background:#f4be4f}.mock-dot.g{background:#61c554}
.mock-url{flex:1;margin-left:8px;height:20px;background:var(--bg-canvas);border:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-radius:6px;padding:0 10px;display:flex;align-items:center;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);max-width:320px}
.mock-body{padding:20px 24px}
.mock-section-eyebrow{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
.mock-h{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:26px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;color:var(--fg-primary);margin-top:2px}
.mock-card{background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:14px 16px}
.mock-card .label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
.mock-card .num{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:28px;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.015em;color:var(--fg-primary);margin-top:4px}
.mock-card .num small{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);margin-left:4px;letter-spacing:0}
.mock-card .delta{font-size:11px;margin-top:6px}
.delta.pos{color:var(--success)}.delta.neg{color:var(--danger)}
.member-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
.member-row:first-child{border-top:0}
.avatar{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;flex-shrink:0}
.avatar.m1{background:var(--member-1)}.avatar.m2{background:var(--member-2)}
.member-row .name{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;flex:1}
.member-row .val{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.bars{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;height:64px;padding-top:4px}
.bars .b{flex:1;min-width:6px;background:var(--brand-500);border-radius:2px 2px 0 0;opacity:0.85}
.bars .b.expense{background:var(--chart-expense)}.bars .b.income{background:var(--chart-income)}.bars .b.saving{background:var(--chart-saving)}
.hero-mini-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:10px;margin-top:14px}
.hero-mini-label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
.hero-mini-num{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:-0.01em}
.hero-mini-num small{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);margin-left:2px}
/* ── 6-FEATURE GRID ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.features-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0;margin-top:var(--space-8);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-left:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg-surface);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md)}
@media(min-width:720px){.features-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
@media(min-width:1024px){.features-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
.feature-cell{padding:var(--space-8) var(--space-8) var(--space-10);border-right:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-3);position:relative;transition:background var(--dur-base) var(--ease-out)}
.feature-cell:hover{background:var(--bg-surface-2)}
.feature-cell .icon{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:var(--radius-md);background:color-mix(in oklch,var(--brand-500) 8%,transparent);color:var(--brand-500);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:var(--space-4)}
.feature-cell .icon svg{width:18px;height:18px}
.feature-cell.ai .icon{background:color-mix(in oklch,var(--accent-500) 14%,transparent);color:var(--accent-600)}
.feature-cell .eyebrow{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
.feature-cell h3{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:26px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;line-height:1.15;color:var(--fg-primary);margin-top:2px}
.feature-cell p{color:var(--fg-secondary);font-size:var(--text-base);line-height:1.55;margin-top:var(--space-2)}
.feature-cell .detail{margin-top:auto;padding-top:var(--space-5);font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.04em;color:var(--fg-tertiary);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.feature-cell .detail .dot-live{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--success);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px color-mix(in oklch,var(--success) 18%,transparent)}
/* ── FEATURE DEEP DIVES ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.feature{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space-10);align-items:center}
@media(min-width:980px){.feature{grid-template-columns:5fr 7fr;gap:var(--space-16)}.feature.reverse>:first-child{order:2}}
.feature+.feature{margin-top:var(--space-24)}
.feature-copy h3{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-3xl);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--fg-primary);margin-top:var(--space-3)}
.feature-copy p{margin-top:var(--space-5);color:var(--fg-secondary);font-size:var(--text-md);line-height:1.55}
.feature-list{margin-top:var(--space-6);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-3);list-style:none;padding:0}
.feature-list li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;font-size:var(--text-base);color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.feature-list .check{flex-shrink:0;width:22px;height:22px;margin-top:1px;border-radius:50%;background:color-mix(in oklch,var(--brand-500) 12%,transparent);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--brand-500)}
.feature-list .check svg{width:12px;height:12px}
.feature-list b{color:var(--fg-primary);font-weight:500}
.feature-mock{background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg);overflow:hidden}
/* ── PHONE MOCKUP ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.phone{width:320px;margin:0 auto;background:oklch(0.14 0.012 250);border-radius:44px;padding:12px;box-shadow:var(--shadow-xl),0 0 0 1px oklch(0.30 0.012 250) inset;position:relative;aspect-ratio:9/19;max-width:100%}
.phone-screen{width:100%;height:100%;border-radius:34px;background:linear-gradient(160deg,oklch(0.42 0.06 252) 0%,oklch(0.32 0.04 252) 60%,oklch(0.22 0.02 252) 100%);overflow:hidden;position:relative;color:#fff;padding:20px 14px 14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.phone-notch{position:absolute;top:12px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:100px;height:26px;background:oklch(0.10 0.012 250);border-radius:13px;z-index:2}
.phone-status{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;padding:0 8px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.phone-status .icons{display:inline-flex;gap:5px;align-items:center}
.phone-status svg{width:14px;height:14px}
.phone-lock-time{text-align:center;margin-top:24px;position:relative;z-index:1}
.phone-lock-date{font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:14px;font-weight:500;opacity:0.85}
.phone-lock-clock{font-family:var(--font-ui);font-weight:200;font-size:72px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:1;margin-top:2px}
.phone-notifs{margin-top:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;flex:1}
.phone-notif{background:color-mix(in oklch,oklch(0.18 0.012 250) 70%,transparent);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-radius:16px;padding:10px 12px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:28px 1fr auto;gap:8px;align-items:center}
.phone-notif .app-icon{width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:7px;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#5C7AE0,#2A3F9E);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff}
.phone-notif .app-icon svg{width:16px;height:16px}
.phone-notif .title{font-size:12px;font-weight:600}
.phone-notif .time{font-size:11px;opacity:0.7;font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums}
.phone-notif .body{grid-column:2/-1;font-size:12px;opacity:0.92;line-height:1.35;margin-top:2px}
.phone-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 24px;margin-top:auto}
.phone-bottom button{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);border:0;backdrop-filter:blur(20px);color:#fff;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}
.phone-bottom svg{width:18px;height:18px}
/* ── AI SECTION ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.ai-section{background:var(--bg-band);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
.ai-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space-12);align-items:center}
@media(min-width:980px){.ai-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:var(--space-16)}}
.ai-mock{background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-xl);padding:var(--space-8);box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg)}
.ai-mock-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding-bottom:var(--space-5);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);margin-bottom:var(--space-6)}
.ai-source{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;white-space:nowrap}
.ai-source .pulse{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent-500)}
.health-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:var(--space-6)}
.health-donut{position:relative;width:144px;height:144px;flex-shrink:0}
.health-donut svg{width:100%;height:100%;transform:rotate(-90deg)}
.health-donut .track{fill:none;stroke:var(--bg-surface-2);stroke-width:12}
.health-donut .arc{fill:none;stroke:var(--success);stroke-width:12;stroke-linecap:round}
.health-donut .center{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center}
.health-donut .score{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:48px;line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--fg-primary)}
.health-donut .max{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.10em;color:var(--fg-tertiary);margin-top:6px}
.health-label .label-text{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
.health-label .label-h{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:28px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin-top:4px;color:var(--fg-primary)}
.health-label .grade-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:var(--space-4) 0 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.health-label .grade-list li{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.health-label .grade-list .pip{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--success);flex-shrink:0}
.health-label .grade-list .pip.warn{background:var(--warning)}
.health-label .grade-list .num{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);white-space:nowrap}
.ai-quote{margin-top:var(--space-6);padding-top:var(--space-6);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
.ai-quote .role{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.10em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent-600);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.ai-quote .role::before{content:"";width:14px;height:14px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#D97757,#C25B36);border-radius:4px;display:inline-block}
.ai-quote blockquote{margin:var(--space-3) 0 0;font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:-0.005em;color:var(--fg-primary);font-style:italic}
.ai-quote .meta{margin-top:var(--space-4);font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:var(--fg-muted);text-transform:uppercase}
/* ── NOTIF LIST ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.notif-list{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:var(--space-8) 0 0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-4)}
.notif-list li{display:grid;grid-template-columns:36px 1fr auto;gap:var(--space-4);align-items:center;padding:var(--space-4) 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
.notif-list .stamp{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--bg-surface-2);color:var(--brand-500);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
.notif-list .stamp svg{width:16px;height:16px}
.notif-list .copy{font-size:var(--text-base);color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.notif-list .copy b{color:var(--fg-primary);font-weight:500}
.notif-list .when{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.06em}
/* ── FÖR VEM ────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.who{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space-4);margin-top:var(--space-8)}
@media(min-width:880px){.who{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
.who-card{background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);padding:var(--space-8);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.who-card::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:3px;background:var(--member-1)}
.who-card.m2::before{background:var(--member-2)}
.who-card.m3::before{background:var(--member-4)}
.who-card .scenario{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
.who-card h4{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:24px;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin-top:4px}
.who-card .quote{margin-top:var(--space-4);font-family:var(--font-display);font-style:italic;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.who-card .by{margin-top:var(--space-5);font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--fg-tertiary)}
/* ── PRINCIPER ──────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.principles{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:0;margin-top:var(--space-8);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
@media(min-width:880px){.principles{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.principles>*:nth-child(2n){border-left:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}}
.principle{padding:var(--space-8) 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);padding-right:var(--space-8)}
@media(min-width:880px){.principles>*:nth-child(2n){padding-left:var(--space-8);padding-right:0}}
.principle .label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent-600)}
.principle h4{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:26px;margin-top:6px;letter-spacing:-0.015em;color:var(--fg-primary)}
.principle p{margin-top:var(--space-3);color:var(--fg-secondary);line-height:1.55;max-width:56ch}
/* ── FAQ ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.faq{margin-top:var(--space-8);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle)}
.faq details{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-subtle);padding:var(--space-5) 0}
.faq summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:var(--space-6);font-size:var(--text-lg);font-family:var(--font-display);letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--fg-primary)}
.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
.faq summary .plus{width:26px;height:26px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:50%;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:var(--fg-secondary);flex-shrink:0;transition:transform var(--dur-base) var(--ease-out)}
.faq details[open] summary .plus{transform:rotate(45deg)}
.faq details[open] summary{color:var(--brand-500)}
.faq p{margin-top:var(--space-3);color:var(--fg-secondary);max-width:70ch;line-height:1.6}
/* ── CTA BAND ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.cta-band{margin-top:var(--space-16);padding:var(--space-20) var(--space-12);background:var(--bg-band);border:1px solid var(--border-subtle);border-radius:var(--radius-2xl);display:grid;gap:var(--space-8);grid-template-columns:1fr;align-items:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
@media(min-width:880px){.cta-band{grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr}}
.cta-band::after{content:"";position:absolute;right:-120px;top:-120px;width:360px;height:360px;background:radial-gradient(closest-side,color-mix(in oklch,var(--accent-500) 35%,transparent) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
.cta-band h2{font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.02em;font-weight:400;position:relative;z-index:1}
.cta-band h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--brand-500)}
.cta-band-side{position:relative;z-index:1}
.cta-band-side p{color:var(--fg-secondary);margin-bottom:var(--space-5)}
/* ── FOOTER ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
.footer{margin-top:var(--space-20);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);padding:var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-10)}
.footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:var(--space-10);align-items:flex-start}
@media(max-width:720px){.footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
.footer-brand p{margin-top:var(--space-4);font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--fg-tertiary);max-width:38ch}
.footer-col h5{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--fg-tertiary);margin-bottom:var(--space-4)}
.footer-col ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-2)}
.footer-col a{font-size:var(--text-sm);color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.footer-col a:hover{color:var(--fg-primary)}
.footer-bottom{margin-top:var(--space-12);padding-top:var(--space-6);border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--fg-tertiary);letter-spacing:0.04em}
/* ── RESPONSIVE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
/* ── RESPONSIVE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
@media(max-width:880px){.nav-links{display:none}}
@media(max-width:980px){.nav-actions .btn-ghost{display:none}}

/* Tablet + small desktop */
@media(max-width:720px){
  /* Layout */
  .wrap,.wrap-narrow{padding:0 var(--space-5)}
  .section{padding:var(--space-16) 0}
  .section-tight{padding:var(--space-12) 0}
  .section-title{font-size:clamp(32px,9vw,52px)}
  .section-lead{font-size:var(--text-base)}

  /* Topbar */
  .topbar-inner{padding:12px var(--space-5)}
  .nav-actions{gap:var(--space-2)}
  .btn-sm{height:34px;padding:0 12px;font-size:12px}

  /* Hero */
  .hero{padding:var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-8)}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(40px,11vw,64px)}
  .hero-lead{font-size:var(--text-base);max-width:100%}
  .hero-eyebrow{font-size:12px;padding:5px 12px 5px 5px}
  .hero-cta{flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-2)}
  .hero-cta .btn{width:100%;justify-content:center}
  .hero-form{flex-direction:column;padding:10px;border-radius:var(--radius-xl)}
  .hero-form input{padding:8px 12px}
  .hero-form button{width:100%}
  .hero-meta{gap:var(--space-5)}

  /* Hero visual — dölj korten på mobil, texten + formuläret räcker */
  .hero-visual{display:none}

  /* Features */
  .feature-cell{padding:var(--space-6) var(--space-6) var(--space-8)}
  .feature+.feature{margin-top:var(--space-16)}
  .feature-copy h3{font-size:clamp(28px,8vw,38px)}

  /* Phone mockup */
  .phone{width:260px}

  /* AI section */
  .ai-mock{padding:var(--space-5)}
  .health-donut{width:120px;height:120px}
  .health-donut .score{font-size:38px}

  /* Who cards */
  .who-card{padding:var(--space-6)}

  /* Principles */
  .principle{padding:var(--space-6) 0;padding-right:0}

  /* FAQ */
  .faq summary{font-size:var(--text-base)}

  /* CTA band */
  .cta-band{padding:var(--space-10) var(--space-6);border-radius:var(--radius-xl)}
  .cta-band h2{font-size:clamp(30px,9vw,48px)}

  /* Footer */
  .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:var(--space-8)}
  .footer-bottom{flex-direction:column;gap:var(--space-2);text-align:center}
}

/* Small phones (iPhone SE etc.) */
@media(max-width:400px){
  .wrap,.wrap-narrow{padding:0 var(--space-4)}
  .topbar-inner{padding:10px var(--space-4)}
  .brand-pill-text{font-size:18px}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(36px,12vw,52px)}
  .nav-actions .btn{display:none} /* bara temat på allra minsta */
  .nav-actions .theme-toggle{display:inline-flex}
}
/* Download cards */
.download-card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;background:var(--bg-surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:18px 20px;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;transition:box-shadow var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out),border-color var(--dur-fast) var(--ease-out)}
.download-card:hover{border-color:var(--brand-500);box-shadow:var(--shadow-md)}
.download-card-icon{width:36px;height:36px;flex-shrink:0;color:var(--fg-secondary)}
.download-card-title{font-size:var(--text-base);font-weight:500;color:var(--fg-primary);line-height:1.2}
.download-card-meta{font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--fg-muted);margin-top:2px}
@keyframes shimmer{0%,100%{opacity:.5}50%{opacity:1}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOPBAR -->
<header class="topbar" role="banner">
  <div class="topbar-inner">
    <a href="#top" class="brand-pill" aria-label="Nidero">
      <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="10"   y="38" width="6.5" height="12" rx="3.25" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.50"/>
        <rect x="19.5" y="32" width="6.5" height="18" rx="3.25" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.65"/>
        <rect x="29"   y="25" width="6.5" height="25" rx="3.25" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.80"/>
        <rect x="38.5" y="18" width="6.5" height="32" rx="3.25" fill="currentColor"/>
        <rect x="48"   y="13" width="6.5" height="37" rx="3.25" fill="#FFD9A0"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="brand-pill-text">Nidero</span>
    </a>
    <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Sektioner">
      <a href="#funktioner">Funktioner</a>
      <a href="#notiser">Notiser</a>
      <a href="#ai-analys">AI-analys</a>
      <a href="#fragor">Vanliga frågor</a>
      <a href="/blog">Artiklar</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a href={APP_URL} class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Logga in</a>
      <a href="#cta" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Anmäl intresse
        <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="top">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span><strong>Byggt för svenska familjer.</strong> Tidig tillgång just nu.</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Ordning på<br/><em>familjens</em> ekonomi.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">Nidero samlar budget, sparande, lån och tillgångar på ett ställe. Så att ni alltid vet var ni står — och vart ni är på väg.</p>
      <form class="hero-form" id="heroForm" onsubmit="return submitWaitlist(event,'hero')">
        <label class="sr-only" for="heroEmail">E-postadress</label>
        <input id="heroEmail" type="email" required placeholder="din@email.se" autocomplete="email"/>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Kom med på väntelistan
          <svg class="arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </button>
      </form>
      <p class="hero-form-note mono">INGEN SPAM · BARA ETT MEDDELANDE NÄR NIDERO ÄR REDO.</p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <div class="label">Sparat 12 mån</div>
          <div class="value">+82 400 <span class="mono muted" style="font-size:14px;">kr</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <div class="label">Konton i översikt</div>
          <div class="value">14</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-meta-item">
          <div class="label">Finansiell hälsa</div>
          <div class="value">74<span class="mono muted" style="font-size:14px;">/100</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero visual: layered cards -->
    <div class="hero-visual" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="hero-card-3 mock">
        <div class="mock-section-eyebrow">Konto · ISK</div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:6px;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;">257 100 <span class="mono" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);">kr</span></div>
            <div class="delta pos mono" style="font-size:11px;margin-top:4px;">+4,2 % i år</div>
          </div>
          <div class="avatar m2" style="width:22px;height:22px;font-size:10px;">S</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card-2 mock">
        <div class="mock-section-eyebrow">Senaste 6 mån</div>
        <div class="bars" style="margin-top:8px;">
          <div class="b income"  style="height:40%"></div><div class="b expense" style="height:32%"></div><div class="b saving" style="height:8%"></div>
          <div class="b income"  style="height:44%"></div><div class="b expense" style="height:36%"></div><div class="b saving" style="height:9%"></div>
          <div class="b income"  style="height:48%"></div><div class="b expense" style="height:30%"></div><div class="b saving" style="height:12%"></div>
          <div class="b income"  style="height:52%"></div><div class="b expense" style="height:38%"></div><div class="b saving" style="height:14%"></div>
          <div class="b income"  style="height:50%"></div><div class="b expense" style="height:34%"></div><div class="b saving" style="height:16%"></div>
          <div class="b income"  style="height:56%"></div><div class="b expense" style="height:36%"></div><div class="b saving" style="height:20%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mono" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:10px;color:var(--fg-tertiary);margin-top:6px;">
          <span>Nov</span><span>Dec</span><span>Jan</span><span>Feb</span><span>Mar</span><span>Apr</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-card mock">
        <div class="mock-chrome">
          <div class="mock-dots"><span class="mock-dot r"></span><span class="mock-dot y"></span><span class="mock-dot g"></span></div>
          <div class="mock-url">app.nidero.se</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mock-body">
          <div class="mock-section-eyebrow">Översikt · Maj 2026</div>
          <div class="mock-h">Hushållet</div>
          <div class="hero-mini-grid">
            <div><div class="hero-mini-label">Netto in</div><div class="hero-mini-num" style="color:var(--success);">+124 300<small>kr</small></div></div>
            <div><div class="hero-mini-label">Buffert</div><div class="hero-mini-num">78 500<small>kr</small></div></div>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:18px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
            <div class="mock-section-eyebrow">Familjen</div>
            <div style="margin-top:8px;">
              <div class="member-row"><div class="avatar m1">A</div><div class="name">Anders</div><div class="val">+ 68 900 kr</div></div>
              <div class="member-row"><div class="avatar m2">S</div><div class="name">Sara</div><div class="val">+ 55 400 kr</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FUNKTIONER -->
<section class="section" id="funktioner">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Funktioner</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Allt ni behöver. <em>Inget</em> ni inte behöver.</h2>
      <p class="section-lead">Nidero är byggt kring hur svenska familjer faktiskt tänker på pengar — inte hur banker vill att ni ska tänka.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feature-cell">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M8 3v4M16 3v4"/></svg></div>
        <div class="eyebrow">01 · Månadsbudget</div>
        <h3>Löner, utgifter och sparkvot — per person.</h3>
        <p>Registrera inkomster och utgifter per familjemedlem. Nidero räknar ut vars och ens andel automatiskt baserat på era löner och visar sparkvoten månad för månad.</p>
        <div class="detail">SPARKVOT · 12 MÅN</div>
